And reset.. 
> Feb 12 13:45:38 porte_de_clignancourt_nds_b kernel:
> hda: status timeout: status=0x80 { Busy }
> Feb 12 13:45:38 porte_de_clignancourt_nds_b kernel:
> hda: drive not ready for command
> Feb 12 13:45:38 porte_de_clignancourt_nds_b kernel:
